      "text": [
        "4220 - وَ - سَأَلَهُ سَعِيدٌ اَلْأَعْرَجُ : عَنْ سُؤْرِ اَلْيَهُودِيِّ وَ اَلنَّصْرَانِيِّ أَ يُؤْكَلُ أَوْ يُشْرَبُ قَالَ \"لاَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4220 - Sa'id al-A'raj asked Imam (as) about the leftover (drink or food) of a Jew or a Christian: \"Is it permissible to eat or drink from it?\"\nImam (as) said: \"No.\""
        ]
      }
    }
